transcript_chunks.text: I got to play two to three hours of Spider-Man 2. it was it was a lengthy demo one of the best demos I've ever played and I was impressed with the variety of it of how many of the different types of uh gameplay elements we're gonna see in this game as both miles and Peter how they're very similar but also very different in terms of their their combat and even traversal the Spider-Man gameplay refined way further than we've ever seen it before and I feel like that's in terms of the momentum of traversal in terms of the variety of the side quests that you're doing in the open world in terms of the characters and stories that they're they're building out there then when you're in the open world you can switch back and forth between them buried GTA 5 but just Lightning Fast playing this I was like I cannot wait every single thing possible in this game it's more Spider-Man that's what this is I think that that's gonna make a lot of people extremely happy I don't know what else they would
